verbose_text: High mitochondrial gene expression was significantly associated with IDH and PBRM1 mutant samples and low expression with FGFR2-fusion samples (XREF_FIG and depicted as a condensed " mitochondrial score " in XREF_FIG); these correlations were improved by removing low-purity (< 0.65) samples, a possible confounding factor (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
